      {/* Modified: 隐藏 Certifications 模块（原作者认证占位），保留结构不删除 */}
      {/* <Section title='Certifications'>
        <Card
          as='a'
          heading='Lorem ipsum'
          subheading='你可以在以下平台找到我： Ex dicat impedit mel, at eum oratio possit voluptatum. Dicat ceteros cu vim. Impetus fuisset ullamcorper pri cu, his posse iisque ad, aliquam honestatis usu id.'
